00:20:35,040 --> 00:20:36,960
Don't shake him. You can't
shake him. Don't move.

261
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:39,040
Xiao Heyun.

262
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:40,840
His breathing is weak.

263
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:42,840
- Sir, stop the bus!
- Wake up.

264
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:43,920
- Someone is sick!
- Sir!

265
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:45,640
- Sir, stop the bus.
- Xiao Heyun.

266
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:46,920
Stop the bus. Someone is sick!

267
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:49,216
- Xiao Heyun, don't scare me.
- He's dying. He can't breathe.

268
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:51,440
Wake up, Xiao Heyun.

269
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:54,760
Stop yelling.

270
00:20:54,840 --> 00:20:56,520
He's awake.

271
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,320
Let me see.

272
00:20:58,920 --> 00:20:59,920
Little girl,

273
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:01,920
does he have some
kind of illness?

274
00:21:02,920 --> 00:21:03,920
It's okay.

275
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:06,200
I'm fine.

276
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,280
Do you call that fine?

277
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,640
You almost stopped breathing.

278
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:10,400
It was just sleep paralysis.

279
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,320
Sleep paralysis?

280
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:14,960
What kind of power put you into
paralysis in broad daylight?

281
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:16,560
Don't talk nonsense.

282
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:18,360
Little girl.

283
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:20,360
You have to take
him to the hospital.

284
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:22,800
Young people these days
are under a lot of stress.

285
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:24,400
Problems develop easily.

286
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,960
Don't let your guard down.

287
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:29,160
Look how scared your
girlfriend is. She's so pale.

288
00:21:30,760 --> 00:21:32,240
Do you need any medicine?

289
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,880
No, thank you.

290
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:34,880
It's okay, ma'am.

291
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:37,480
I have all kinds
of medicine here.

292
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:39,160
Just tell me if
you need anything.

293
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:46,760
You really scared me just now.

294
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:48,720
I thought you wouldn't wake up.

295
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:52,480
I could hear you,

296
00:21:52,560 --> 00:21:53,880
but I just couldn't wake up.

297
00:21:55,560 --> 00:21:58,480
Were you stuck in standby mode?

298
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:02,280
Thank goodness you woke up.

299
00:22:02,360 --> 00:22:05,040
I don't know what I'd
do if I were alone.

300
00:22:06,760 --> 00:22:08,440
It just hit me in the face.

301
00:22:08,520 --> 00:22:10,360
It hurts so much.

302
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:17,040
How long have you been awake?

303
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:21,120
When I woke up,

304
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,680
it was the same as last time.

305
00:22:22,760 --> 00:22:25,400
The time didn't move up.
They were already on the bus.

306
00:22:32,760 --> 00:22:33,840
That means

307
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:38,320
once the bomb is on the
bus, the time won't move up.

308
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:45,280
Xiao Heyun.

309
00:22:46,280 --> 00:22:48,240
If the time doesn't
move up anymore,

310
00:22:50,600 --> 00:22:52,080
then has the time loop

311
00:22:52,560 --> 00:22:53,560
ended too?

312
00:22:55,520 --> 00:22:57,920
If the time loop ends,

313
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,000
then…

314
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:01,320
Then this is our last
chance to get off the bus.

315
00:23:11,240 --> 00:23:13,920
It's also the last chance of
survival for the people on this bus.

316
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:26,880
What…

317
00:23:27,960 --> 00:23:28,960
What should we do?

318
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,720
Are we…

319
00:23:48,560 --> 00:23:50,440
Are we really getting off?

320
00:23:55,160 --> 00:23:56,760
Haven't we already decided?

321
00:24:04,080 --> 00:24:06,560
Actually, I want to live too.

322
00:24:07,240 --> 00:24:09,440
I'm human. I'm
afraid of dying too.

323
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:11,640
Actually…

324
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:15,520
I wanted to get off every time.

325
00:24:16,120 --> 00:24:18,000
I even secretly thought

326
00:24:18,840 --> 00:24:22,080
that I could take
advantage of this time loop

327
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:24,480
to do something outrageous
and unrestrained.

328
00:24:25,560 --> 00:24:28,320
For example, I don't have to worry
about spending too much money.

329
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:31,120
I can eat and drink all I want
without worrying about gaining weight.

330
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:32,960
Or…

331
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:35,440
I can stay up all night
at an Internet café

332
00:24:35,520 --> 00:24:37,920
without going back to my dorm.

333
00:24:40,840 --> 00:24:44,560
But those are the only
things I can think of

334
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,000
that could make me happy.

335
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,960
I'm just an ordinary person.

336
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:52,880
I can only imagine so much.

337
00:24:53,360 --> 00:24:54,560
But I think…

338
00:24:58,000 --> 00:25:00,240
If we can save the
people on this bus,

339
00:25:02,840 --> 00:25:06,360
that's the most outrageous and
unrestrained thing I can think of.

340
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:10,520
Moreover, right now,

341
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:14,160
they are no longer
strangers to me.

342
00:25:31,280 --> 00:25:33,080
ROUTE 45 TO XUEYE SOUTH ROAD

343
00:25:39,040 --> 00:25:40,280
I'm not getting off.

344
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:42,720
I'm sorry.

345
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:03,200
<i>We've arrived at
Yanjiang East Road.</i>

346
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:05,656
- Let's try one last time.
<i>- Please exit through the rear door.</i>

347
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:09,520
<i>Please tap your card when
exiting. Please mind the doors.</i>

348
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:23,720
Sir, don't close the
door yet. Wait a moment.

349
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:25,760
- We dropped something.
- Thank you.

350
00:26:25,840 --> 00:26:26,880
We have to look for it.

351
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:28,440
- Hurry up.
- Okay.

352
00:26:31,520 --> 00:26:32,520
Young man.

353
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:34,000
Are you feeling better?

354
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:37,160
- I'm fine now.
- Don't forget to go to the hospital.

355
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:38,240
Okay.

356
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,440
What are you looking for?

357
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:42,880
If it's nothing important,
don't look for it.

358
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:43,960
I lost my flash drive.

359
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:46,096
- Very important documents are on it.
- A flash drive?

360
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:47,160
You have to find it then.

361
00:26:47,240 --> 00:26:48,560
What color is it?

362
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:51,520
It's about the same
color as the floor.

363
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:52,840
So it's gray.

364
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,200
A flash drive?

365
00:26:54,280 --> 00:26:55,576
- I don't see a flash drive.
- No.

366
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:57,200
Help them find it.

367
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:58,760
It's not at the front.

368
00:26:58,840 --> 00:27:00,240
I'm sorry, you…

369
00:27:01,760 --> 00:27:03,080
What's happening?

370
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,560
- Why are you stealing?
- What are you doing?

371
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:06,680
- Go!
- Xiao Heyun!

372
00:27:06,760 --> 00:27:08,000
Go!

373
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:11,680
Xiao Heyun!

374
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:15,160
There's a murderer!

375
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,400
Run!

376
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:22,360
Open the door, sir!

377
00:27:30,520 --> 00:27:33,080
Help her!

378
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:22,800
Help her!

379
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:37,320
Don't let her pull it!

380
00:28:41,080 --> 00:28:43,400
Don't let her pull it!

381
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,640
ROUTE 45 TO XUEYE SOUTH ROAD

382
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:22,760
GANGWU NEW VILLAGE STOP

383
00:29:22,840 --> 00:29:25,920
<i>The bus is moving.
Please hold on tight.</i>

384
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:28,160
<i>Next stop, Yanjiang East Road.</i>

385
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:36,280
Shiqing.

386
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,040
Shiqing.

387
00:29:38,120 --> 00:29:39,120
Wake up.

388
00:29:40,520 --> 00:29:41,600
Wake up!

389
00:30:12,760 --> 00:30:13,760
It's me.

390
00:30:22,560 --> 00:30:23,560
It's okay now.

391
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:25,920
It's okay.

392
00:30:40,840 --> 00:30:46,360
NEXT STOP, YANJIANG EAST ROAD

393
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:55,440
SORT YOUR WASTE, RECYCLE

394
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:06,320
This time, we'll get
off at the next stop.

395
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:08,000
Let's forget about everything.

396
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,440
We still came back after all.

397
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:27,120
Don't think about it.

398
00:31:41,080 --> 00:31:42,840
<i>We've arrived at
Yanjiang East Road.</i>

399
00:31:42,920 --> 00:31:44,400
<i>Please exit through
the rear door.</i>

400
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:46,040
<i>Please tap your
card when exiting.</i>

401
00:31:46,120 --> 00:31:48,760
<i>Please mind the doors.</i>

402
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:05,920
Let's try one more time.

403
00:32:09,120 --> 00:32:10,320
It's not worth it.

404
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:39,560
What happened?

405
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:41,760
Someone died.

406
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,880
There has been a murder!

407
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:44,000
Murder!

408
00:34:44,080 --> 00:34:45,400
- Call the police!
- A murder!

409
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:46,960
Call the hospital! Hurry!

410
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:48,320
Call an ambulance!

